          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Samples were irradiated with and without cadmium",
                " shield. Because 59Co and 197Al have different sensi-",
                " tivities to thermal and epithermal neutrons, monitor",
                " wires allow to determine the thermal and epithermal",
                " fractions of neutron flux"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Monitor samples are cobalt/aluminium and gold/",
                " aluminium wires which were used to monitor neutron",
                " flux at the target positions",
                "-Co/Al alloy(Co 0.46wt%, 0,381 mm in diameter),",
                " Au/Al alloy (Au-0.112wt%,0,510 mm diam)",
                ".Metallic silver foil. The irradiation of the sample",
                " was performed in a hydraulic transfer tube of Kyoto",
                " University reactor with and without cadmium capsule"
              ]
            }
          ],
